                            <h4>Granollers, Cataluyna - Espanya</h4>
                        <p>Carre camp de les moreres, 14 </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                             <p><strong>Tel:</strong> (+34)971336051  |
                             <strong>Fax:</strong> (+34)971330176</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
